verbose_text: Similarly, the proportion of depressed patients did not moderate the association between childhood trauma with and CRP (t = 1.07, P = 0.30, I 2 res = 73.5%, tau 2 = 0.006), IL-6 (t = 0.44, P = 0.66, I 2 res = 47.6%, tau 2 = 0.006) or TNF-alpha (t = 0.22, P = 0.83, I 2 res = 43.3%, tau 2 = 0.01).
